<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Personal Portfolio | Welcome</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* CSS Variables for easy color tweaking */
        :root {
            --bg-color: #fcfaf9;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-main: #2d2d2d;
            --text-secondary: #666666;
            --accent: #8e9aaf; /* Soft slate blue */
            --accent-light: #efeff0;
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem 10%;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            background: rgba(252, 250, 249, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin-left: 2rem;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0 10%;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background-color: var(--text-main);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--accent);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Portfolio/Projects */
        .section {
            padding: 5rem 10%;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .project-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-light);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .project-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .project-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .project-card p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            padding: 5rem 10% 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--accent-light);
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            nav { padding: 1.5rem 5%; }
            .section { padding: 3rem 5%; }
            nav ul { display: none; } /* Simplified for demo */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">YOUR.NAME</div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#work">Work</a></li>
            <li><a href="mailto:hello@example.com">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>Building digital <br> experiences with care.</h1>
        <p>I’m a designer and developer focused on creating clean, user-friendly interfaces that solve real-world problems.</p>
        <div>
            <a href="#work" class="btn">View My Work</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="work" class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Selected Projects</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>01. E-Commerce Flow</h3>
                <p>A minimalist shopping experience designed for high-end boutique brands. Built with React and CSS Grid.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>02. Health Tracking App</h3>
                <p>An intuitive mobile application focused on mental wellness and habit formation tracking.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>03. Portfolio Template</h3>
                <p>A lightweight, light-themed template for creatives and developers to showcase their talent.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="section" style="background-color: var(--accent-light);">
        <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
        <p style="max-width: 800px; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
            With over five years of experience in the industry, I believe that great design is invisible. 
            I spend my time obsessing over typography, whitespace, and the small details that make a user feel at home. 
            When I'm not coding, you can find me hiking or reading about architecture.
        </p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Your Name. Built with curiosity and code.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
